snippet.title: Windowkill v3.0 + Steam Announcement
snippet.description:
Windowkill is getting another major update, and coming to Steam!
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2726450/Windowkill/

Multiplayer, unlocks, game modes, new characters, new enemies, and more... coming soon!

Thanks for the support everyone ❤️
